{"tid":331916,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 10 又有新BUG！越用得多核部腦反而越慢！","createTime":"2017-07-22T14:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T05:46:02.000Z","uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c86bc750c7f0a74782f8567085a23eefdaeb8fd","tid":331916,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>以 Bug 多聞名的 Windows 10 系統又爆出了新問題</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Windows-10-624x351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2FWindows-10-624x351.jpg&h=c6ca8343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2017/07/17/windows-10-brings-bug-again/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2Fwindows-10-brings-bug-again%2F&d=HhOqQxtV6vaMmw0agYn3NPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=f9234ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2017/07/17/windows-10-brings-bug-again/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n近日一名 Google 工程師在工作中發現，他的 Windows 10 系統在 Intel 24 核心 48 線程處理器、64GB 記憶體、高速 SSD 等超強硬體配置下，處理起普通編譯任務時竟然也出現了延遲現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有時竟然連滑鼠也動不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/17133019/CPU1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F17133019%2FCPU1.jpg&h=5c44dc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">程式設計師出身的他立即調出系統管理員查看，卻發現無論 CPU 還是記憶體都並沒有佔滿，很少有超過 50% 的。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n透過查看 Windows 系統事件追蹤工具 ETW，結果發現 Windows 10 在行程銷毀方面的確存在一個嚴重的問題。即當程式／行程需要關閉時，Windows 10 會透過某一單獨線程處理。也就是說即便你有幾十個處理器核心，Windows 10 在關閉行程時也只會調用其中一個，即這時 Windows 10 其實是單線程執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/17132932/CPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F17132932%2FCPU.jpg&h=2fe8addd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n一般情況下這也沒什麼，但對程式設計師來說，頻繁啟動、關閉大量行程是常見的操作，於是悲劇就發生了。且更糟糕的是，<span style=\"color: red;\">該問題在 CPU 核心數越多，關閉和開啟的動作越頻繁的情況下，窒機就越嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span>該工程師面對的問題就是，CPU 高達 48 線程，但銷毀行程時只有 1 個拚命工作，另外 47 個都在圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n經過驗證，這個 Bug 只在 Windows 10 上存在，舊版本的 Windows 7 反而沒有問題。目前，他已經將該 Bug 告知微軟。"},{"pid":"ed0cba135351e463717f79afcc2cd99d2d897972","tid":331916,"uid":50818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76adf4f61d8448c31934e2bc78f8fa46c6b475e7","tid":331916,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778af58b1ff05b21214e6a4928f312e1516a550e","tid":331916,"uid":50801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"十足啲無能主管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老細請大堆人翻嚟，但派工果陣就將工作責晒落一個人做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd3e3a055462364349c47750f4207fd2f493450","tid":331916,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 48線程，我屋企都淨係8線程"},{"pid":"7c8bc318e8da8dd